%^YELLOW%^Skill: Academics

%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^A player's academics skill indicates the book learning and general knowledge of the character. It would cover areas of writing, arithmetic, knowledge of history and other academic pursuits including, but not limited to, the following: engineering, geography, geology, geometry, probability, local knowledge, logic, military tactics, monster lore, nature lore, nobility lore, planar lore, religious lore.

%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Stat basis: %^WHITE%^intelligence
%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Current areas of influence: %^WHITE%^writing, reading, forgery, item lore

%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Related helpfiles: %^WHITE%^skills, write, sign, study
